page.title: 05A TYPICAL DAY(GIRL) FORRES E
page.content: On Monday morning I get up at 7.30am I wash , dress and have my breakfast I have cornflakes and tea. If I have enough time before I go to school I make my bed. I then meet Wendy at the bottom of the road at 8.30am.School starts at 8.45am.We have 80mins of music first thing then we have 40mins of french after that 15mins break after that we have 40mins of geography after that we have modern studies. After modern studies we have lunch from 1'O clock till 2.10. We have science till 3.30 then I walk home with Wendy.I get home at 3.40pm.At about 5.00pm I have my dinner and watch TV and at about 10.30pm I go to bed then I listen to my tapes.
